Revision history for Devel-Platform-Info
========================================

0.15    2014-10-06
        - fixed license fields in META.json to be lists.
        - added latest Mac OS X release.
        - fixed Linux release notes.

0.14    2014-05-09
        - last two release missed updating DPI::Mac. #RT95491 (thanks to Kent 
          Fredric).
        - fixed META tests to catch version differences.

0.13    2014-05-07
        - parse out OpenIndiana variant of Solaris (thanks to Graham Ollis,
          sorry it got missed out of the last release).
        - added experimental support for BeOS.
        - more Linux based OSes.

0.12    2014-05-06
        - fixed distribution name in META.
        - added LICENSE file.
        - in the event of error, return the message in the data returned.
        - Linux codenames update.
        - Mac OSX codenames update.

0.11    2012-10-03
        - fixed require
        - added Test::MockObject::Extends prerequisite.
        - added Colin's PAUSE id.
        - change file dates changed to meet W3CDTF standards.
        - implemented Perl::Critic suggestions.

0.10    2012-06-05
        - updated BSD derivative list.
        - fixed OpenSolaris/Solaris oslabel/osvers elements.
        - added Red Hat Enterprise Linux & Red Hat Linux codenames.
        - added CrunchBang Linux codenames.
        - updated versions and codenames.
        - META tests no longer require specific versions.
        - added minimum perl version (5.006).
        - reworked Makefile.PL for clarity.
        - Test-JSON-Meta => Test-CPAN-Meta-JSON.

0.09    2011-05-25
        - remove trailing newlines from Mac command results (JJ)

0.08    2011-04-01
        - added Scientific Linux distro (as suggested by Norbert Gruener).

0.07    2011-01-13
        - updated several distribution codenames (Linux & Mac).
        - documentation update.

0.06    2010-07-15
        - added requirement for Test-JSON-Meta-0.08 due to issues with old
          versions of JSON not implementing the current API.
            - better 32/64 detection for BSD (thanks to Chris Williams for help)
            - upped version check of Test-JSON-Meta to ensure we have JSON v2.

0.05    2010-07-12
        - updated Mac version check (Colin Newell).
        - added Mac tests (Colin Newell).
        - updated diag reference test (Colin Newell).

0.04    2010-07-04
        - fixed Solaris internal references.
        - fixed BSD kernel version formatting.
        - changed 'source' to be a hash not a string. (Colin's suggestion).

0.03    2010-07-02
        - added support for more known Linux distributions.
        - better pattern matching for osvers and oslabel in Linux.pm
        - added reference links.
        - reimplemented use tests for plugins.
        - added specific support plugin for Solaris family.

0.02    2010-07-01
        - added support for Irix and the BSD family.

0.01    2010-06-30
        - initial release.
